Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/calm_mind">Calm Mind</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/calm_mind">Calm Mind</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user quietly focuses its mind and calms its spirit to raise its Sp. Atk and Sp. Def stats.</p>